---
title: Cheesy BBQ Double Beef Bowls with Buttery Charred Corn and Rice
description: Bowls are perfect for quick weekday meals and this one will be a hit with the whole family! Lean ground beef is tossed in BBQ sauce, then spooned over buttery rice. Charred corn adds some extra comfort to this bowl!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/bols-au-boeuf-bbq-et-au-fromage-ab073b55-d44753b8.jpg
